list.comment:

Refreshed .nupkg files for Compression, Encryption, Extension, Extension.ServiceCollection, Validation, and Wrapper. These updates likely include changes to binaries or metadata to reflect the latest adjustments in the respective components.

task.summary:
Refactor and reorganize ETAMP example projects
Moved and restructured ETAMP example project files for better modularity and project clarity. Updated project references and dependencies to align with the new structure. Removed redundant files and added missing configurations where necessary.

Refactor and reorganize ETAMP example projects
Moved and restructured ETAMP example project files for better modularity and project clarity. Updated project references and dependencies to align with the new structure. Removed redundant files and added missing configurations where necessary.

Refactor and reorganize ETAMP example projects.
Restructured and cleaned up ETAMP example project files for improved clarity and maintainability. Updated project references, adjusted configurations, and removed redundant code. Minor formatting fixes and consistency improvements were also applied.

Add CreateSignETAMPService project and update dependencies
Introduced the CreateSignETAMPService project to the solution for improved modularity. Updated related configurations, project dependencies, and code to support the new functionality. Minor adjustments were made to existing services for consistency.

Add CreateSignETAMPService project for modularity
Introduced the CreateSignETAMPService project to enhance solution structure and maintainability. Updated dependencies, project configurations, and integrated related services. Minor changes were made to existing components for consistency.

Add region directives and ECDsaRegistration implementation
Region directives were introduced across multiple files to improve code organization and readability. An `ECDsaRegistration` class was implemented for better management of ECDsa providers. The changes also include minor adjustments to parameters and accessibility levels for consistency and maintainability.

Refactor ECDsa management and remove deprecated classes.
Removed ECDsaCreator and ECDsaKeyManager classes along with their interfaces. Introduced ECDsaStore and refactored ECDsaProviderBase with support for flexible ECDsa management. Updated dependencies and adjusted implementations where necessary.

Refactor ECDsa management and add comprehensive documentation.
Replaced deprecated ECDsa key management classes with modular implementations like `ECDsaStore` and enhanced `ECDsaProviderBase`. Improved flexibility in ECDsa handling by integrating named and GUID-based storage mechanisms. Updated codebase with extensive XML documentation for better code clarity and maintainability.

Refactor ETAMP services and enhance ECDsa management.
Renamed service implementations for better readability and modularity, aligning class names with their respective functionalities. Refactored ECDsa handling by introducing modular components like `ECDsaStore` and improving `ECDsaProviderBase`. Improved flexibility, added comprehensive XML documentation for maintainability, and updated dependencies accordingly.

Remove obsolete ETAMP example projects and refactor structure.
Deleted outdated ETAMP example projects, including CreateETAMP, CreateSignETAMP, and ValidateETAMP. This change streamlines the codebase by removing redundant files and unused dependencies. Updated structure and configurations to improve clarity and maintainability.

Refactor project structure and rename key components.
Reorganized namespaces, classes, and files for better alignment and clarity. Renamed "CreateETAMPService" to "CreateETAMP", "CreateSignETAMPService" to "SignETAMP", and adjusted all references accordingly. Updated solution and project files to reflect the new structure.

Refactor ETAMP project structure and update README.
Reorganized namespaces, classes, and project files for better alignment and clarity. Renamed key components like `CreateETAMPService` to `CreateETAMP` and updated solution references. Overhauled README to reflect the changes and provide updated usage examples.

Add NuGet packaging support and update ETAMP project details
Enabled automatic NuGet package generation for all ETAMP projects with output to a unified `nupkgs` directory. Updated copyright year to 2025 and adjusted project metadata for clarity and consistency. Prepared the solution for streamlined deployment and distribution.

Add NuGet packaging support and update project metadata.
Enabled automatic NuGet package generation for all ETAMP projects, outputting to a unified `nupkgs` directory. Updated project files to include README linking and adjusted metadata for consistency. Prepared the solution for streamlined deployment and better package clarity.

Add NuGet packaging support and update project metadata.
Enabled automatic NuGet package generation for all ETAMP projects, outputting to a unified `nupkgs` directory. Updated project metadata for consistency, including README linking and package references. Adjusted dependencies and configurations for streamlined deployment and improved clarity.

Update project version to 1.0.1
Incremented the version from 1.0 to 1.0.1 in the project file. This change likely reflects minor updates or fixes to the project. No other modifications were made in this commit.

Update .nupkg files for multiple ETAMP components
Refreshed .nupkg files for Compression, Encryption, Extension, Extension.ServiceCollection, Validation, and Wrapper. These updates likely include changes to binaries or metadata to reflect the latest adjustments in the respective components.
